      "message": "Remigiusz has right. Currently if you edit config map and break it, you  don't catch exception and it won't be work.\nProposed composition class with  CbsClientConfigMap and CbsClientRest allow to read configuration in steps: \n1. Read config map -> if break ...\n2. Make REST Request -> if break ...\n3. Read default config.",
