      "message": "Ok. Fine for me, consider if that should change anything e.g. if ConfigMap should appear between creating the CbsClientImpl and using the method get.\nMoving this call to the constructor would reduce the number of fields of the class (only field needed would be CbsClientSource) and there would be no need for null check.\n(feel free to mark the comment as resolved if no changes will be applied)",
